'''John Russell''' is an [[United States|American]] [[Contract bridge|bridge]] player.

==Bridge accomplishments==

===Wins===

* [[North American Bridge Championships]] (1)
** [[Leventritt Silver Ribbon Pairs]] (1) 1997 

===Runners-up===

* [[North American Bridge Championships]] (1)
** [[Leventritt Silver Ribbon Pairs]] (1) 2003 

